lect points of interest\n\u2022 Shoot photos to share with friends\n\u2022 Download only the locations you wish to see\n\u2022 Regular content updates with more locations to come\n\nCurrent Locations:\nHorseshoe Bend, White Pocket, Mount Morrison, Mount Whitney, Alabama Hills, The Wave, Arches National Park, Death Valley National Park (North & South), Antelope Canyon, Crystal Crag, Haifoss Iceland, and more locations coming soon.", "short_description": "BRINK Traveler is a virtual travel experience that takes you to amazing natural locations in full 3D to feel like you're really there. Step into a postcard and visit some of the most breathtaking places on Earth today!\n\nFeaturing:\n\u2022 18 incredible spots to see across 12 locations\n\u2022 A virtual guide to teach you about your surroundings\n\u2022 Collect points of interest\n\u2022 Shoot photos to share with friends\n\u2022 Download only the locations you wish to see\n\u2022 Regular content updates with more locations to come"}]}, "developer_name": "BRINK XR", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.BrinkXR.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.BrinkXR.com/terms", "publisher_name": "BRINK XR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.BrinkXR.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "726368587961803"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["TRAVEL", "EXPLORATION", "EDUCATIONAL"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "GAMEPAD_VIA_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE", "SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_US